	(11284,73,'page_header','Who We Are'),
	(11285,73,'page_sub_header','BrainDo is a full-service, interactive agency with one goal: <strong>Help Our Clients Succeed Online.</strong>'),
	(11286,73,'first_paragraph','BrainDo is a collection of hard working go-getters and experts that come together to create great things for our clients. Our experience lets us cut through the fads and develop the strategy and tactics that truly work to build brand experience and bring measurable results.'),
	(11287,73,'paragraph_header_1','We Get It.'),
	(11288,73,'paragraph_text_1','Our brains arent wired faster, we just care more about getting it right. Our team understands how to grow, sustain and reimagine digital brands. We draw on our combined expertise of 50+ years in Digital Marketing having touched on nearly every vertical including: Travel, Automotive, Insurance, Legal, Pharmaceutical, Ecommerce, B2B, Health/Beauty & Fitness and Entertainment.'),
	(11289,73,'paragraph_header_2','We Get It Done.'),
	(11290,73,'paragraph_text_2','The number one reason our clients like us, put simply, We Get it Done. Great strategy doesnt mean squat if you cant execute  and we execute with precision. We believe clients have the right to great results in a timely fashion and we continue to be the agency known for getting it done and doing it well.'),
