	(11411,104,'page_header','Advanced Analytics'),
	(11412,104,'page_sub_header','Unlocking the Potential of our Client\'s Data'),
	(11413,104,'challenge_header','Challenge:'),
	(11414,104,'challenge_content','<p><span class=\"tx\">Our clientneeded a unifying structure to implement its analytics across its websites. It often led to</span><span class=\"tx\">confusion during analysis and left gaps of incomplete data. Inconsistent use of custom events,</span><span class=\"tx\">variables and goals made analysis difficult or sometimes impossible.</span></p>'),
	(11415,104,'solution_header','Solution: '),
	(11416,104,'solution_content','<p><span class=\"tx f910\">Apply the BrainDo full host of advanced analytics solutions to assess our client\'s analytics need</span><span class=\"tx\">and roll out the updated tags and analytics measures to improve the</span><span class=\"tx f910\">brands overall</span><span class=\"tx\">performance.</span></p>'),
	(11417,104,'results_header','Results:'),
	(11418,104,'results_content','<p><span class=\"tx\">BrainDo implemented an overhaul of their analytics tagging including an optimized user interface</span><span class=\"tx\">that allowed our client to gather more reliable data and access it more intuitively.</span><br /><span class=\"tx\">Analytics Implementation of:</span></p><ul><li><span class=\"tx\">Google Tag Manager, which fires Universal and Classic calls to GA</span></li><li><span class=\"tx\">Consistency of custom events, variables and goals</span></li><li><span class=\"tx\">Site Search</span></li><li><span class=\"tx\">Ecommerce</span></li><li><span class=\"tx\">Google Web Master Tools</span></li><li><span class=\"tx\">Form field, form submission, cross domain, download link, telephone link, external link </span></li><li><span class=\"tx\">55 Custom Events</span></li><li><span class=\"tx\">10 Custom Variables</span></li><li><span class=\"tx\">5 Content Groups</span></li><li><span class=\"tx\">Custom Channel Groupings</span></li><li><span class=\"tx\">10 Goals</span></li><li><span class=\"tx\">5 Filters</span></li><li><span class=\"tx\">Page View customization</span></li><li><span class=\"tx\">Complete Parity of Universal and Classic</span></li><li><span class=\"tx\">Custom Event-driven 3rd Party Tag Tracking</span></li></ul><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span class=\"tx\">Improving the consistency, breadth and depth of our client\'s</span><span class=\"tx f910\">analyti</span><span class=\"tx\">cs allows them to dig deeper,</span><span class=\"tx\">finding better answers more efficiently. Measurement plans were now more straight-forward and</span><span class=\"tx\">product level analysis was more clear and concise.</span></p>'),
	(11419,104,'case_study_image_url','case-study-analytics.jpg'),
	(11420,104,'background_image','cs-analytics.jpg'),
	(11421,104,'background_video',''),
	(11422,104,'use_case_image','/infographics/use-case-analytics.jpg'),
	(11435,110,'page_header','Engaging a Social Audience.'),
	(11436,110,'page_sub_header','We created the most engaging and far reaching and engaging campaign our client had ever seen. '),
	(11437,110,'challenge_header','Challenge: '),
	(11438,110,'challenge_content','<p><span class=\"tx\">Our clients Facebook fans numbered around 20,000 but were primarily composed of current</span><span class=\"tx\">customers and employees. The core audience was moderately active, yet rarely generated</span><span class=\"tx f5\">much social reach among non-fans. The organic reach of posts was about 45% lower than</span><span class=\"tx\">the clients Facebook fan base.</span></p>'),
	(11439,110,'solution_header','Solution: '),
	(11440,110,'solution_content','<p><span class=\"tx\">We created a social media campaign centered around an interactive quiz that highlighted one of</span><span class=\"tx f910\">the clients new products in an education, fun way. We designed &amp;</span><span class=\"tx\">developed the quiz as well</span><span class=\"tx\">as additional education content, social posts and supported the endeavor with social media and</span><span class=\"tx\">paid ads.</span></p>'),
	(11441,110,'results_header','Results:'),
	(11442,110,'results_content','<p class=\"tb f5\"><span class=\"tx\">Through an engaging social campaign we generated a total reach of 700k+ across all social</span><span class=\"tx\">platforms. The top Facebook posts attracted 5x more clicks than any previous post, organic</span><span class=\"tx\">daily reach rose by 117% and Facebook fans increased by 7%. Twitter saw a similar boost to</span><span class=\"tx\">engagement and an increase of 14% new Twitter followers.</span></p><ul><li class=\"tb f5\"><span class=\"tx\">Social Stats: 19 days before the campaignaverage daily organic reach of 7,270</span></li><li class=\"tb f5\"><span class=\"tx\">19 days of the campaign  average daily organic reach of 15,797 (117% rise)</span></li><li class=\"tb f5\"><span class=\"tx\">19 days after the campaignaverage daily organic reach of 8,664 (return to pre-campaign levels)</span></li></ul><p class=\"tb f5\"></p><p class=\"tb f5\"><span class=\"tx\">Paid content increased reach further. Over 48k people per day were reached using Facebook</span><span class=\"tx\">and Twitter ads. This was the most far reaching and engaging social media campaign our client</span><span class=\"tx\">had ever produced.</span></p>'),
