	(324,1,'2014-11-13 08:05:51','2014-11-13 13:05:51','<a href=\"http://dev.brain.do/wp-content/themes/BrainDo/library/images/blog/introducing-new-website.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-310\" src=\"http://dev.brain.do/wp-content/themes/BrainDo/library/images/blog/introducing-new-website.jpg\" alt=\"introducing-new-website\" width=\"848\" height=\"284\" /></a>\r\n\r\nWere happy to announce the launch of the new and improved BrainDo <a href=\"http://www.brain.do\">website</a>! The new site has been a long time coming and were proud of the final product. It gives visitors a good look at our offerings, our work and most importantly, the answer to the age old question: Who is BrainDo?\r\n\r\nCheck it out at <a href=\"http://www.brain.do\">www.brain.do</a>!\r\n<h4>About BrainDo</h4>\r\nBrainDo has grown tremendously in the past year and weve made sure that our website reflects the entire team - <a href=\"brain.do/about-us\">who we are</a> and <a href=\"brain.do/services\">what were capable of</a>. Consider this our official HELLO! to the world.\r\n\r\nWere all about no-nonsense digital marketing. We care deeply about the work we do and invest in our clients business as if it were our own. Were a collection of talented individuals who know how to take brands to the next stage of their digital evolution.','Introducing, the New and Improved BrainDo Website!','','inherit','open','open','','290-revision-v1','','','2014-11-13 08:05:51','2014-11-13 13:05:51','',290,'http://dev.brain.do/290-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
